item.title: Trying GoLang for the first time
item.description: As someone who has been involved in software development for over 3 years, I have primarily worked with JavaScript -and nowadays Typescript mostly- although I have also used languages like Python for specific projects. In this article, I want to share my initial impressions of the Go programming language as a web developer. I don’t intend for this to be a negative critique of JavaScript, as there are already plenty of those.
